The possibility of the ballots in Michoacán individually auszuzählen is being considered
According to the information from "preparatory conference, the difference between the first and second place in the election of the Governor nearly 27 percent, with a total of 879 votes have been counted 6074 not yet.
The possibility of Einzelauszählung of ballots in this year's elections in Michoacán a reality, because under the Programa de Resultados Electorales Preliminares ("preparatory conference) issued data, the difference between the first and second place in the gubernatorial elections nearly 27 percent, with a total of 879 votes have been counted 6074 not yet.
In this sense, the President of the Consejo General del Instituto Electoral de Michoacán (IEM), María Ángeles de rid Llanderal Zaragoza, remember that just last November 9, the electoral body a set of rules on the harmonisation of local rules with the reforms of the federal states in electoral matters had passed.
It should be remembered that Michoacán neither his political constitution nor his electoral law nor its law on the election law passed by Congress in the reforms had adapted so that those in this round of elections were not in force. The Governor Leonel Godoy Rangel avoided their publication in the Official State Gazette within the designated time with the argument that still objections.
On 9 November, the Supreme Court ruled Mexico (SCJN) on the local legislature's constitutional complaint and keep the voice of the state to the constitutional reforms as "invalid and illegal," because it does not have the right to 'veto or to decide against it. "
María Ángeles de rid Llanderal said in an interview on the possibility of Einzelauszählung of votes that, thanks to the adoption of the directives by the Consejo General del IEM is the possibility that the local electoral authority the ballot counting in part or in full.
Under the following conditions can in one or more electoral votes are counted packages contained some of the results in the Minutes do not agree; the Protocol on the vote count and berechnung lies not in terms files or it is not in possession of the chairman of the electoral commission, or there are obvious errors or changes in the protocols.
In addition, the total count of ballot papers will be full pressure, if there is a difference between the alleged winners and, in the second place, which are equal to or less than one per cent is provided at the beginning of the session is an explicit request of party-or coalition from above, the second of these candidates.
The vote count could also be in their entirety if, after the conclusion of the proper calculation says that the difference between the alleged winners and the candidates in the second place equal or less than one percent, provided it is an explicit request from a representative of the party whose candidate Second, above, in which case the election packages, which suffered a partial count were excluded.
It is worth noting that the elections in Morelia in the same situation, where under "preparatory conference of the difference between the first and second place just 0.16%, although the voices of 129 out of a total of 923 election protocols have not yet been counted.
